name: Warung Passion
address: Delod Uma, Jl. Mulioto, Buwit, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: Great place, well priced. Good English tasty food, beautiful staff. Great views from the roof top dining of rice fields & mountains in the distance. Fruit & vegetables harvest from the gardens you can see.
review 2: The food amazing. Make me addicted to it! The service super friendly, the view wow factor! Addictive spot and food! Highly recommended!
review 3: Warung Passion is a hidden gem I discovered while on a jog through the rice paddies of Buwit. Mbak Desak has always extended graceful hospitality. Her enthusiasm for people and place is highly contagious. Warung Passion is a great showcase of what Baliâ€™s fertile soil can yield.
review 4:
If you're looking to do a short day trip or are heading towards Tanah Lot there's a unique opportunity to visit a little known piece of paradise in Kaba Kaba.
Warung Passion is nestled amongst the rice paddies. Food is ridiculously cheap and utterly delicious. Am posting pics and a short video. You can look on their website or FB page for menu and directions of how to get there.
Aahh the serenity.
review 5:
Delicious food, good price, so relexing place.
The Owner and her family super friendly. We really enjoy hangout here at Warung Passion.
